# cherub.word — the gate, right below I. Processes the three BE ops (birth/connect/release) and summon:mate — a connected name births its first top-level being through cherub, owned by the name. Descends from able.word.

A cherub is an able.
A cherub can do grant-able:human.
A cherub can do grant-able:global.
A cherub can call mate as receiver.
A cherub can be birth.
A cherub can be connect.
A cherub can be release.
A cherub needs scripted cognition.
A cherub never wakes.
